528
00:39:51,951 --> 00:39:53,384
"We are alive.

529
00:39:56,791 --> 00:39:58,564
"Please don't give up on us."

530
00:40:03,016 --> 00:40:04,081
It's perfect, Claire.

531
00:40:13,410 --> 00:40:15,957
You know, I'm not giving up
on you either, Charlie.

532
00:40:18,896 --> 00:40:19,951
It's gonna be okay.

533
00:40:20,940 --> 00:40:22,051
You'regonna be okay.

534
00:40:28,604 --> 00:40:30,381
We'll get through this together.

535
00:41:18,381 --> 00:41:19,381
What?

536
00:41:21,679 --> 00:41:22,679
We're here.

